{{Otheruses|staff}}
A '''stun-staff''' was a large melee weapon that used the design of primitive [[Staff/Legends|staves]], but produced a shock on one end when they touched an opponent. These were similar in appearance and function to [[Stun baton/Legends|stun batons]]. [[Ulban Arms/Legends|Ulban Arms']] [[S-EP1 security droid]]s each carried a stun staff, and were certified experts in their use.<ref name="EGTD">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref>

